TEXT.S: = Su'aci = Gaga mniq Kawsyungsu Tawyuncyu ka alang Su'aci. 22 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 84 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 88% niqan 74 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 12% niqan 10 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Bunun 30%, Rukai 7%, Cou 19%, Hla'alua 30%, Amis 2%.
